  "instructions": [
    "Heat rapeseed oil in a skillet over medium heat.",
    "Sear plantain slices until caramelized, about 5 minutes per side.",
    "Sauté mirepoix until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add glass jelly and stir to combine with mirepoix.",
    "Season with cilantro, lime juice, salt, black pepper, ginger, garlic, turmeric, cumin powder, oregano, and paprika.",
    "Transfer mixture to a dolsot stone bowl.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with additional cilantro if desired."
